---
import '@fontsource/inter/400.css';
import '@fontsource/lora/400.css';
import '@fontsource/lora/600.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>All These Difficult Human Realities Inspirational — Oyparaploo</title>
<style>
*,*::before,*::after{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
*{font-style:normal;}
body{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,#000000 0%,#020203 20%,#060810 40%,#0a0d16 60%,#0d111b 80%,#111521 100%);background-attachment:fixed;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:80px 40px;}
.piece{max-width:580px;width:100%;}
.title{font-family:'Lora',serif;font-size:clamp(22px,2.5vw,28px);font-weight:600;color:#d0c8bf;letter-spacing:0.02em;margin-bottom:48px;opacity:0;animation:breathIn 2s ease forwards;}
.breath{font-size:1.0588rem;font-weight:400;color:#b5ada5;line-height:1.75;letter-spacing:0.01em;margin-bottom:20px;opacity:0;animation:breathIn 1.8s ease forwards;}
.breath:last-of-type{margin-bottom:0;}
.breath .debut{color:#ccc5bc;font-weight:450;}
.ellipsis{color:#a09888;letter-spacing:0.25em;}
.turn{text-align:center;font-size:1rem;color:#8a8078;letter-spacing:0.35em;margin:44px 0;user-select:none;line-height:1;opacity:0;animation:breathIn 1.8s ease 0.5s forwards;}
.breath:nth-of-type(1){animation-delay:0.6s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(2){animation-delay:0.9s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(3){animation-delay:1.2s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(4){animation-delay:1.5s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(5){animation-delay:1.8s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(6){animation-delay:2.1s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(7){animation-delay:2.4s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(8){animation-delay:2.7s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(9){animation-delay:3.0s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(10){animation-delay:3.3s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(11){animation-delay:3.6s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(12){animation-delay:3.9s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(13){animation-delay:4.2s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(14){animation-delay:4.5s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(15){animation-delay:4.8s;}
.breath:nth-of-type(16){animation-delay:5.1s;}
@keyframes breathIn{from{opacity:0;}to{opacity:1;}}
.colophon{margin-top:64px;height:1px;border:none;background:#5a5048;opacity:0;animation:breathIn 2s ease 5.7s forwards;}
@media(max-width:480px){body{padding:48px 24px;}.title{animation-duration:1s;}.breath{animation-duration:1s;}.turn{animation-duration:1s;}.breath:nth-of-type(1){animation-delay:0.3s;}.breath:nth-of-type(2){animation-delay:0.45s;}.breath:nth-of-type(3){animation-delay:0.6s;}.breath:nth-of-type(4){animation-delay:0.75s;}.breath:nth-of-type(5){animation-delay:0.9s;}.breath:nth-of-type(6){animation-delay:1.05s;}.breath:nth-of-type(7){animation-delay:1.2s;}.breath:nth-of-type(8){animation-delay:1.35s;}.breath:nth-of-type(9){animation-delay:1.5s;}.breath:nth-of-type(10){animation-delay:1.65s;}.breath:nth-of-type(11){animation-delay:1.8s;}.breath:nth-of-type(12){animation-delay:1.95s;}.breath:nth-of-type(13){animation-delay:2.1s;}.breath:nth-of-type(14){animation-delay:2.25s;}.breath:nth-of-type(15){animation-delay:2.4s;}.breath:nth-of-type(16){animation-delay:2.55s;}.turn{animation-delay:0.25s;}.colophon{animation-delay:3.0s;animation-duration:1s;}}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="piece">
  <h1 class="title">All These Difficult Human Realities Inspirational</h1>

  <p class="breath">here is how it happened</p>

  <div class="turn" aria-hidden="true">*</div>

  <p class="breath">We want to make art that we can live with when we're older <span class="ellipsis">...</span> what a challenge</p>

  <div class="turn" aria-hidden="true">*</div>

  <p class="breath"><span class="debut">It's mostly an evolution of making and starting place of something fresh <span class="ellipsis">...</span> Living in the realm of possibilities is carrying hope</span></p>

  <div class="turn" aria-hidden="true">*</div>

  <p class="breath">We show and interpret disasters <span class="ellipsis">...</span> in order for lesser privileged people to be able to comprehend any of it <span class="ellipsis">...</span></p>

  <p class="breath">Entertainment distractions of <span class="ellipsis">...</span> every direction and from every perspective <span class="ellipsis">...</span> every awake hour of the day</p>

  <p class="breath">The thought of going further down in Earth's geological layers and extracting shell crude oil <span class="ellipsis">...</span></p>

  <p class="breath">There's the prevailing argument that if it wasn't the United States, it would have for sure been someone else <span class="ellipsis">...</span></p>

  <div class="turn" aria-hidden="true">*</div>

  <p class="breath">We are outsiders moving into a stream <span class="ellipsis">...</span> Linking moments to what we fully sense <span class="ellipsis">...</span></p>

  <div class="turn" aria-hidden="true">*</div>

  <p class="breath">Yes and no. Yes empathy <span class="ellipsis">...</span> No comfort <span class="ellipsis">...</span> Yes unbridled character <span class="ellipsis">...</span> No shelter <span class="ellipsis">...</span></p>

  <p class="breath">Door bored hole brrd <span class="ellipsis">...</span> backwards and upside down <span class="ellipsis">...</span></p>

  <p class="breath">We're essential searching for food like a pack of night hyenas so to speak <span class="ellipsis">...</span></p>

  <div class="turn" aria-hidden="true">*</div>

  <p class="breath">Let's bring back what has been diminished <span class="ellipsis">...</span> for head locks <span class="ellipsis">...</span></p>

  <p class="breath">During this crisis <span class="ellipsis">...</span> dancing to an uplifting song can immediately reduce pain and increase the best type of suffering <span class="ellipsis">...</span></p>

  <hr class="colophon" aria-hidden="true">
</div>

</body>
</html>